Title: Dochamon Junior
Description: ['Japan has 47 prefectures and each one has a guardian spirit called a Dochamon. ', Dochamon Junior, ' follows guardian spirits in training to one day take over the jobs of their elders. But these juniors have a lot of growing up to do before they graduate!']
